data.description: Looking for a spacious and comfortable home with plenty of room for your family?   This Redland Estates 5-bedroom home is the perfect choice.   This home boasts large and comfortable rooms that are perfect for families of all sizes. The backyard is wonderful and perfect for outdoor activities. The master suite is large and comfortable, with plenty of space, and a large walk-in closet. The other four bedrooms are also spacious and comfortable, with large closets and plenty of natural light.  The living & dining areas are also large and perfect for entertaining. The living room is warm and inviting, with a cozy fireplace. Spacious and functional Kitchen, with plenty of upgraded counter space and storage.
